Package com.halcyoninae.halcyon.constant

Class Global

java.lang.Object
com.halcyoninae.halcyon.constant.Global
public class Global extends Object
This class holds any public scoped Objects that may be used throughout the program.

This class eliminates different classes having to hot potato pass difference object instances to each other.

Since:
3.0
Author:
Jack Meng
